=== The Tower ===
1. '''''The Tower''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 5 ''"Attempt to communicate with the creature."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Binary Communication'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Observe the creature and report back."'', proceed to  '''''A Long Awaited Welcome'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 5 ''"Kill it."'', available IF homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Fish in a Barrel'''''

2a. '''''Binary Communication''''', gives {{reward|soc|rsh2|empty|empty}}

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Invite them aboard."'', proceed to '''''Playing Host'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Offer something in return."'', costs 100 {{iconify|Alloys}}, proceed to '''''Reciprocity'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 0 ''"Leave the site."'', proceed to '''''Prophecy Rejected'''''

2b. '''''A Long Awaited Welcome''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Invite them aboard."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Playing Host'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Offer something in return."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, costs 100 {{iconify|Alloys}}, proceed to '''''Reciprocity'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 0 ''"Leave the site."'', proceed to '''''Prophecy Rejected'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 5 ''"Kill the creature."'', available IF homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Fish in a Barrel'''''

3. '''''Fish in a Barrel''''', gives {{reward|uni|rsh4|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''Prophecy Rejected'''''

4a. '''''Playing Host'''''

* ''"Invite them to our empire."'', gives a new Scientist of The Tower's species in one year with the {{trait|Society Focus|34px|bg=soc|veteran=yes|link=}} [[Scientist traits#Analyst traits|Society Focus]] and {{trait|resilient|Increased Lifespan|w=34px|link=}} [[Common leader traits#Special traits|Increased Lifespan]] traits, '''ends the rift'''
* ''"Confiscate their documents and release them."'', gives a random {{iconify|Society}} [[Society research|Technology]], '''ends the rift'''

4b. '''''Reciprocity''''', gives {{reward|uni|rsh4|empty|empty}}, '''ends the rift'''

4c. '''''Prophecy Rejected''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast3|empty|empty}}, '''ends the rift'''
